**Reduction Lemma (claim).** Suppose the **core estimate** holds:
  (★)  `‖P(P(x)∘b) − P(x∘b)‖ ≤ O(η)·‖x‖·‖b‖`   for `b∈A` and `x` a `•`/`∘`-monomial in elements of A.
